repository.name: JobTH-Implementation
repository.description: Job search system. Project after studying THiNKNET bootcamps. Use microservice architecture. Using React(Next.js), Redux, Styled components, Ant design, GraphQL, Node.js(Express), MongoDB, Redis(Rate limiter at API Gateway), Elasticsearch, RabbitMQ, Cloudinary(File storage), AWS SES. Deployed to K8s.
